descriptionHtml:
Dunmer face preset for CharGen.

Required Mods:

SKSE: http://skse.silverlock.org/
SkyUI: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?
RaceMenu Mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624//?
ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?
Ethereal Elven Overhaul: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?

Recommended Mods:

Textures:
I'm using a mix of Eryniel's texture and Mature Skin.

Hairs:
Lovely Hairstyles CE: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=221168621

Eyes:
The Eyes Of Beauty: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
Brows: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?

Lightning Effects

Enhanced Lights and FX: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27043/?
BLEAK ENB - UNBLEAK ENB: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24828/?

Instructions:

After downloading and installing all mods mentioned above.
Follow these steps:

1. Download my mod and install it at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
2. Open Skyrim using SKSE
3. Load any working save file
4. Open the console
5. Type showracemenu
6. Select the Dark Elf (Dunmer) Race
7. Look for the slide option "preset slot"
8. Select the slot 30 and press F9, this should load my character's face.
9. Customize your character as you please
author: shadowfake aka taveira
